The paper discusses the integration of cloud computing and Internet of Things, which involves distributed systems, networking, software engineering, systems and control, and cybernetics. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing), followed by cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), cs.SE (Software Engineering), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.CY (Cybernetics).
